longBusinessSummary: Sinolink Worldwide Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, invests in, develops, manages, and sells real estate properties in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Property Development, Property Management, Property Investment, Financing Services, and Others segments. The company provides property leasing services; engages in the provision of property management, multiple consultancy, and project management services; and operates hotel and primary schools, as well as finance leasing solutions. It also provides loan financing, business factoring, administrative service supporting, and consultancy services in relation to information, multimedia, and communication technologies. Sinolink Worldwide Holdings Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.
